*********************************************************
  This  folder contains XSLs Gsearch to transform FOXML
  from Fedora Repository to Solr index XML.
*********************************************************


Content:
*********************

./includes  : contains further xsl files which are included
./templates : useful templates example and templates for xslt


Configuring gsearch:
*********************

all configuration regarding indexing is found in
fedora/tomcat/webapps/fedoragsearch/WEB-INF/classes/fgsconfigFinal/index/FgsIndex/

By default, foxmlToSolrDemo.xslt is used. And it can be configured in index.properties.

The xslt to be used can be configured by the propery fgsindex.defaultUpdateIndexDocXslt

Every modification needs to restart Tomcat.